{"tid":145820,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"想買部山狗，幫手睇睇抵唔抵屌","createTime":"2017-03-06T14:13:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T07:11:35.000Z","uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40778b1dabef97b4f223162ad94fcf2689f8e8f1","tid":145820,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T14:13:34.000Z","msg":"Let x=r<br />\n我嚟緊5月會去台灣玩8日，當中會玩啲比較戶外嘅活動，好似潛水同高卡車之類，就想買部山狗拍吓片。<br />\n<br />\n咁我知得sjcam 呢個牌子先係&quot;正版&rdquo;嘅山狗，就想買sj5000x elite 呢個model.<br />\n有4K@24fps,2K@30fps同1080P@60fps，仲有gyro 影像穩定功能咁。<br />\n<img src=\"http://ecx.images-amazon.com/images/I/41LVAwMyPwL._SX300_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fecx.images-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FI%2F41LVAwMyPwL._SX300_.jpg&h=cfa09d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n詳細spec : <a href=\"http://www.sjcamhd.com.hk/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=88&amp;search=sj5000x+elite\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sjcamhd.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Froute%3Dproduct%2Fproduct%26product_id%3D88%26search%3Dsj5000x%2Belite&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=5d9bd018\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sjcamhd.com.hk/index.php?route=product/product&amp;product_id=88&amp;search=sj5000x+elite</a><br />\n<br />\n上網就見到鴨記有間地鋪賣緊$728，想問吓各位巴打有冇係鴨記一間叫<br />\n&quot;Fxee Zone&quot;嘅舖頭買過山狗？<br />\n唔知有冇大伏。<br />\n<br />\nbetween, 我發現有啲自己廠整gopro 配件嘅淘寶店，賣嘅配件就當然唔係正版，不過啲質素應該都夠用。<br />\n不過平嘅程度係離曬譜，正版一條頭帶買兩舊幾，間鋪買十幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，買完山狗喪入配件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8ca0725de3e433dcb5c0a94fa84295a5dc1e8a","tid":145820,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"364df5f5f8d8eeecc91b6d14a18014b5bc2212f2","tid":145820,"uid":56095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1df5071e680488e297b6a568b682cd609d738f52","tid":145820,"uid":87270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:09:21.000Z","msg":"唔抵，其實真山狗又好 假山狗又好，都係山寨野，ssp四五百都有部所謂嘅&quot;4K&quot;"},{"pid":"c7c3de3dd810dea9b020919bdd416fc44f32421b","tid":145820,"uid":87270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"4k得24fps，最多都係影到靜態<br />\n如果淨係用一兩次，問人借或者租仲好"}]}